{"tid":1514413,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"「港人自救！」暫停對外捐獻，先救深陷囹圄嘅手足！","createTime":"2019-08-28T17:25:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T15:42:22.000Z","uid":15567,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"94b803a2e43a76db9cb639b9c2165e822f0485d1","tid":1514413,"uid":15567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:25:23.000Z","msg":"港人樂善係人人皆知<br />\n每年捐款以十數億計<br />\n<br />\n依家手足齊心抗暴政<br />\n唔少人被捕急需支援（不論法律支援/生活開支/醫療費用）<br />\n<br />\n我係度呼籲大家<br />\n暫停其他慈善機構捐款<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">先將自己嘅善心交俾手足</span></span><br />\n捐俾你認為信得過嘅組織或機構<br />\n幫助每一位抗爭者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家每次想捐錢<br />\n就諗下現時香港實在有太多抗爭者需要大家協助<br />\n一分一毫都幫到忙<br />\n盡自己一分力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地要真正做到<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">No One Left Behind</span></span><br />\n<br />\n#港人自救<br />\n#先救手足<br />\n#香港人道危機"},{"pid":"1aff7527d53bf584439f91a4a7d53c11357f2de1","tid":1514413,"uid":28921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:28:41.000Z","msg":"推啊！<br />\n救左自己屋企先啊！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59cfa433433fdc66250eb09e3b95d93a8b3d65dc","tid":1514413,"uid":21483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:29:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d1b0bd966b277968de26c086f33da64530f8890a","tid":1514413,"uid":31655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:32:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"635b78bbca1229cc586f9c53775834441423101b","tid":151